::KitKat::

She watched Land Mine run to her room.  She looked at Time Bomb.
She sighed,"I don't how, but I am going to make you both understand. 
Hurting yourselves, and getting hurt isn't a good thing.  I don't 
know how you last leader was or how he did things.  But I doo things 
very differently from your last leader. I care about you two and 
don't want to see either of you get hurt.  OK? I won't hurt you as a 
form of punishment.  I'd have both of you scrubbing the walls of the 
base with a toothbrush before I'd hurt either of you."
